{"tid":995277,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《東京喰種》神曲《Unravel》TK from凜冽時雨　巡演4月抵港","createTime":"2019-01-25T10:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T14:27:50.000Z","uid":55179,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb2b2b3ac01c1384482802d68c92b796a808e097","tid":995277,"uid":55179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T10:14:14.000Z","msg":"《Unravel》主唱TK from 凛として時雨巡演：香港站4月7日星期日​<br />\n<br />\nTK from 凛として時雨（凜冽時雨）主唱之《東京喰種》第一季動畫主題曲《Unravel》都算是撕心裂肺的「爆肺神歌」，Chrous一輪Emo慘情飆高音尖叫吶喊後再來咆哮，道出主角金木研由人變成食屍鬼之歷程，聽到都覺唱到嘔血。無疑，世上只有嗓音聲線中性、剛柔並濟的原作曲者TK（北嶋徹）方能完美駕馭。<br />\n<br />\n《Unravel》已是5年前的作品，石田翠漫畫《東京喰種：re》也於去年夏天迎來大結局，《東京喰種：re》動畫亦已於2018年底播完，TK為最後階段獻唱《katharsis》，成個系列正式曲終人散也。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/遊戲動漫/285622/東京喰種-神曲-unravel-tk-from凜冽時雨-巡演4月抵港\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E5%8B%95%E6%BC%AB%2F285622%2F%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E5%96%B0%E7%A8%AE-%E7%A5%9E%E6%9B%B2-unravel-tk-from%E5%87%9C%E5%86%BD%E6%99%82%E9%9B%A8-%E5%B7%A1%E6%BC%944%E6%9C%88%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF&d=Ev%2FgGGd3hbiNhm%2BUCJXp8MP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=acda913b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/遊戲動漫/285622/東京喰種-神曲-unravel-tk-from凜冽時雨-巡演4月抵港</a>"},{"pid":"9554ddb52e3a76a60cd410e135f6c465c9c2d0da","tid":995277,"uid":55179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T10:14:44.000Z","msg":"想去 但要考試我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41b8ed326fd6aeb9c6e9efcbbbf7dadb59f7d8b","tid":995277,"uid":8511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T10:55:19.000Z","msg":"叫達哥一齊合唱都會諗下去睇"},{"pid":"4fb5f36945addade2b8c72a65c4928ad1213bf38","tid":995277,"uid":41524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T14:27:50.000Z","msg":"沒有春袋的人"}]}